  <name>Simplay is a simple, reusable API for implementing audio playback applications on Android. It is a layer of abstraction above Android's MediaSession API.

By using the MusicService and the optional MediaControlFragment, Simplay allows you to easily stream audio without worrying about the cumbersome MediaPlayer API.</name>
